	dprr:hasNoteText "Quaestor in Africa in the late Republic or the early Augustan period. He was honored by the mancup(es) stipend(forum) ex Africa (CIL 6.31713-ILS 901). See PIR(2) 3.196, no. 462. (RS, MSRP 1.281; TJC)[92x]\n" .
